{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "A crucial step in this quantization scheme is to find a good quantization ranges for the quantizer as noted in [57].",
    "In this quantization scheme no retraining of the LLM is involved.",
    "This method of quantization (specifically the case with data free quantization) is particularly helpful when security or data privacy may limit data access [58].",
    "2) Quantization aware training (QAT) involves in retraining the pre-trained LLM using training data.",
    "In this quantization scheme since the quantization operation is nondifferentiable, during back-propagation the gradient is approximated using an identity function also known as Straight Through Estimator [59]."
  ],
